Hello and welcome to ISP 100,
offered by the Institute for the Study of

24502880-ee0a-4afe-9882-5b5c9336362f-1
00:00:16.262 --> 00:00:18.640
University Pedagogy, or ISUP.

f66e37af-b22f-4fae-9d3a-eb4553f68307-0
